e\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, i saw the orbital line, as seen in the screenshots.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/fnxe1Qd\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EScreenshot Series\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=Probes.json\u0026amp;fileKey=%5B!AES128GCM%5Bi2QX8fHjNuXj4kxIzqO8KCA1Xb6U%2BFWn7IOOsjMLny0VDRooVbSeYAtwWidoTcvRk9dYY/XK2LCQdoPV%5D%5B16432d76e7ad59a51d333cd1%5D%5B897d74cdbd7f88504dfed3fe329ebaae%5D%5D\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EProbes.json\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-29T23:52:59Z\u0022 title=\u002212/29/2023 11:52  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 29\u0022\u003EDecember 29, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Spicat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}